name: 5 Ways to Overcome Anxiety
summary: While we’ve grown and developed as human beings
short_description: While we’ve grown and developed as human beings, a lot of things have carried over since our prehistoric days. The fight or flight response is one of those things that gives you the adrenaline and instincts to tackle a potential problem or run from it to live to fight another day. Unfortunately, some people have difficulty controlling that sense of anxiety, to the point that it negatively affects their well-being. Let’s take a look at some easy ways to overcome your anxiety.
